  task: ffff967af0520000 task.stack: ffffa5f05484000
  RIP: 0010:mutex_lock+0x19/0x20
  Call Trace:
    flush_workqueue+0x81/0x460
    ocfs2_shutdown_local_alloc+0x47/0x440 [ocfs2]
